{"tid":1957703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚德塞拍片大讚習近平有遠見 命清華開公共衛生學院","createTime":"2020-04-04T06:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T07:12:13.000Z","uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"94586c6a2b969a8aa08b786e5bb4260e9cb270f1","tid":1957703,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TRgunXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTRgunXW.png&h=f5aa2c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平上月 2 日視察清華大學時，指要加強中國疫情防控和公共衛生科研，一個月後清華大學拍板成立公共衛生與健康學院，前天（2 日）舉行成立儀式，聘請了 2003 年沙士時任香港衞生署署長、世衛生前總幹事陳馮富珍，為學院首任院長。現任世衞總幹事譚德塞拍片祝賀學院成立，感謝中國國家主席習近平，在加強中國公共衛生方面的領導和遠見。<br />\n<br />\n根據《清華大學網》報道，清華大學公共衛生與健康學院成立儀式前天舉行，以視像會議形式連線北京、深圳、香港三地。報道指，習近平於 3 月 2 日考察清華大學時指，要加強中國疫情防控和公共衛生科研，清華大學黨委經兩次常委會會議後，決定成立公共衛生與健康學院，聘請陳馮富珍為學院院長。<br />\n<br />\n陳馮富珍透過視像致辭，指現時世界各國面臨嚴峻挑戰，防控疫情的發展需要全球共同協作努力。清華大學成立公共衛生與健康學院「恰逢其時」，充分展現清華作為世界一流大學的責任擔當。<br />\n<br />\n陳馮富珍又指，疫情令各界理解國際合作的重要性，學院「就是這次疫情黑夜中升起的一顆啟明星」。<br />\n<br />\n接替陳馮富珍出任世衞總幹事的譚德塞，亦有拍片祝賀學院成立，他感謝國家主席習近平在加強中國公共衛生、應急管理體系建設方面的領導和遠見，也感謝清華大學積極響應習近平的號召，一個月內成立公共衛生與健康學院。"},{"pid":"5de050cc98bd317a55c59fd3aebb796703a3ef94","tid":1957703,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa22be7abe4b5cf228d152d2ac08ab993335c5a","tid":1957703,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a7f57581db9deb36277cd4aaaec2aa62ec83bd","tid":1957703,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bOldJIUGEgM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FbOldJIUGEgM%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6e52cbcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQ3QkqDVAAAb3Uy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEQ3QkqDVAAAb3Uy.jpg&h=05d67613&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92ddfcdd28afc84d5b376da6c31f80822dc14bbd","tid":1957703,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"契弟譚生係咪諗住比人迫落台後去返工"},{"pid":"61a9c52c05d7dbd89a231f854f1a694b836fcded","tid":1957703,"uid":200758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4fbBkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4fbBkd.jpg&h=bb32347f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46ad971a6ce1d328c30e18ebefbaa729d651ab06","tid":1957703,"uid":83609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"屌你比啲非洲貪污豬做國際組織領袖真係陀撚衰全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df48157a405361b6f4a3a459927ba6cabd47d5f","tid":1957703,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"69<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f409bb4142d386ce61ce566251e24c49dc431948","tid":1957703,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f90f1be9f77f2775fc2d612a66ff56cd76b0498","tid":1957703,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"真係笑撚死人,  以為雞珍好有 CREDIT ?"},{"pid":"c4908d0949f683e19eb40006e84dd9d144669f5e","tid":1957703,"uid":219903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"91c1b978f1b7346879f70bde20f3fda91b49611f","tid":1957703,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislik